{"tid":112413,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"C朗為狗場籌款伸援手","createTime":"2017-02-08T06:29:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-08T07:19:10.000Z","uid":14977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"192bfa7cbf98b5381752bffdcd4b93d28b467f07","tid":112413,"uid":14977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T06:29:35.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=sSksRl51obRI29wW5WU5SZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=80ea7a32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】皇家馬德里星級前鋒基斯坦奴朗拿度最近捐出親筆簽名球衣，為祖家葡萄牙國內一個資金匱乏的狗場籌募經費，盡一分力。<br />\n<br />\n身屬皇馬的葡萄牙國家隊隊長基斯坦奴朗拿度（Cristiano Ronaldo）為善最樂，最近亦關顧到愛護動物方面。<br />\n<br />\n事緣葡萄牙國內小區Gouveia有一個可謂避難所的狗場，恆常地照顧多達80頭狗隻。然而，每頭犬隻的照料成本多達2000歐元，對狗場造成嚴峻的財政壓力。狗場的53歲女義工Gloria為此事聯絡C朗家人，結果得到該名射手的正面回應。<br />\n<br />\n雖然沒有直接捐錢，C朗向狗場致送一件簽了名的皇馬7號球衣，為狗場作慈善拍賣之用，協助狗場籌集營運經費。狗場擁有人Liliana接受訪問時則表示：「我從心底感謝（基斯坦奴）朗拿度，這對他來說是舉手之勞，但非常重要。」"},{"pid":"45411f74674fe2fab7632a4320c55c7e60b25c58","tid":112413,"uid":23385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T06:31:27.000Z","msg":"慈善球王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec12a909b94436cc27bb80811df90f1fd8112208","tid":112413,"uid":993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T06:31:47.000Z","msg":"照顧埋同胞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f25a0f32e07d41e5f1752ad34fa5b48fd5d7de92","tid":112413,"uid":22149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T06:35:29.000Z","msg":"以為大劇院個狗場"},{"pid":"44c11fa66916b61b43952f698c8d4f3874544347","tid":112413,"uid":70361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T06:54:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkg